<span id="freeTextContainer2193089313584609129">I think this should be a must read for any person. I grew up knowing absolutely nothing about LGBTQ individuals other than negative comments from those in my rural Southern Baptist Community. At the age of 72 I am learning. Many of the strategies for understanding oneself, dealing with hateful people or bullies, dealing with stress, and making life decisions in general are helpful for all readers of any age although the focus is on teens. The resources provided are excellent. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


