              <span id="reviewTextContainer2580838714" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11075275671871713026">I really should have read this in high school, this was such a good book. It&apos;s very general, but it&apos;s interesting to see how the author tries to touch on so many things.</span>
  <span id="freeText11075275671871713026" style="display:none">I really should have read this in high school, this was such a good book. It's very general, but it's interesting to see how the author tries to touch on so many things.</span>
